The paper focuses on user modeling and personalized suggestions of points of interest based on social information available on location-based social networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category, which deals with the organization, storage, retrieval, and dissemination of information. Additionally, the paper also touches upon social networks (cs.SOC) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC) aspects, as well as data management (cs.DB) and social computing (cs.SI) sub-categories.
